<br>
I would be willing to entertain discussion along those lines, with provisions agreed upon by all in advance.<br>
<br>
Essentially, to create this compromise both sides would need to be willing to give.<br>
<br>
The 'solo killers' would be relenquishing 3 pop advancement mobs (and consequently the quieter exp areas) by allowing alliances to be used, and then broken immediately after.<br>
<br>
The 'duo killers' would need to agree in advance a rather stringent policy, with a stiff penalty for teaming on mobs other than AD, Behe, Grum.  This would quiet the paranoid folks, to a degree.<br>
<br>
I think it's time to open a new thread, perhaps rogg would like to, and start a formal detailed debate of exactly what each party would like from this, without the right wing and left wing mumbo jumbo.<br>
<br>
